\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

 durch 
\begin_inset Formula \[
w(x)=ad_{-f}^{n-1}v(x)\]

\end_inset

definiert.
 Die Behauptung 
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
S^{\prime}(z)\alpha^{(j)}(z_{n},u)=ad_{w}^{j-1}ad_{-F}^{n}v(x,u)\quad\textrm{für}\quad j\geq1\label{eq:claim}\end{equation}

\end_inset

wird mit vollständiger Induktion bewiesen.
 Wegen
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:ad-n"

\end_inset

 gilt Gl.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:claim"

\end_inset

 für 
\begin_inset Formula $j=1$
\end_inset

